0mission%E2%80%99s%20goal%20is%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20dynamics%20of%20several%20solar%20phenomena%20by%20imaging%20and%20measuring%20particles%20in%20the%20sun%E2%80%99s%20upper%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spacecraft%20carries%20seven%20payloads%20to%20observe%20the%20photosphere%2C%20chromosphere%20and%20the%20outermost%20layers%20of%20the%20Sun%2C%20called%20the%20corona%2C%20using%20electromagnetic%2C%20particle%20and%20magnetic%20field%20detectors.%20Four%20payloads%20will%20directly%20view%20the%20Sun%20and%20the%20remaining%20three%20payloads%20will%20carry%20out%20in-situ%20studies%20of%20particles%20and%20fields%2C%20%E2%80%9Cproviding%20important%20scientific%20studies%20of%20the%20propagatory%20effect%20of%20solar%20dynamics%20in%20the%20interplanetary%20medium%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20ISRO.%20The%20space%20agency%20plans%20to%20understand%20phenomena%20like%20the%20problem%20of%20coronal%20heating%2C%20coronal%20mass%20ejection%2C%20pre-flare%20and%20flare%20activities%20and%20their%20characteristics%2C%20and%20the%20dynamics%20of%20space%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02120024%2Faditya-payload.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02120024%2Faditya-payload.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02120024%2Faditya-payload-300x130.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671142%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22443%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAditya%20L1%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20payload.%20Photo%3A%20ISRO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%206