%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02120205%2FScreenshot-2023-09-02-at-11.41.59-AM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02120205%2FScreenshot-2023-09-02-at-11.41.59-AM-300x157.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02120205%2FScreenshot-2023-09-02-at-11.41.59-AM-1024x536.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671143%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20trajectory%20of%20the%20Aditya-L1%20mission.%20Photo%3A%20ISRO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20NASA%20and%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency%20have%20sent%20numerous%20probes%20to%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20solar%20system%2C%20India%20is%20the%20first%20Asian%20nation%20to%20place%20an%20object%20in%20solar%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScientific%20objectives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ISRO%2C%20the%20major%20science%20objectives%20of%20the%20Aditya-L1%20mission%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStudy%20of%20Solar%20upper%20atmospheric%20(chromosphere%20and%20corona)%20dynamics.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStudy%20of%20chromospheric%20and%20coronal%20heating%2C%20physics%20of%20the%20partially%20ionized%20plasma%2C%20initiation%20of%20the%20coronal%20mass%20ejections%2C%20and%20flares.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EObserve%20the%20in-situ%20particle%20and%20plasma%20environment%20providing%20data%20for%20the%20study%20of%20particle%20dynamics%20from%20the%20Sun.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPhysics%20of%20solar%20corona%20and%20its%20heating%20mechanism.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDiagnostics%20of%20the%20coronal%20and%20coronal%20loops%20plasma%3A%20Temperature%2C%20velocity%20and%20density.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDevelopment%2C%20dynamics%20and%20origin%20of%20CMEs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIdentify%20the%20sequence%20of%20processes%20that%20occur%20at%20multiple%20layers%20(chromosphere%2C%20base%20and%20extended%20corona)%20which