y%22%3A%22Lufthansa%20will%20bring%20back%20the%20double%20decker%20Airbus%20A380%20on%20the%20Delhi%20route%20along%20with%20first%20class%20service%2C%20to%20celebrate%20six%20decades%20of%20connecting%20the%20Indian%20capital%20with%20Germany.%20The%20German%20mega%20carrier%20has%20been%20flying%20to%20India%20for%20much%20longer%2C%20including%20doing%20so%20to%20Jodhpur%20in%201934%20with%20a%20JU52.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SAURABH%20SINHA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2F60-years-of-flying-to-delhi-lufthansa-brings-back-a380-first-class-to-this-route%2Farticleshow%2F103301222.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Importance%20of%20Being%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02103657%2FF3uRFgvW8AAhDHt.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20late%2C%20political%20observers%20have%20noticed%20the%20body%20language%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20when%20he%20is%20in%20the%20company%20of%C2%A0%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%20Rahul%20visibly%20displays%20a%20lot%20of%20respect%20and%20reverence%20for%20the%2081-year-old%20Congress%20veteran.%20A%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20Rahul%20made%20a%20public%20gesture%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20he%20sat%20beside%20the%20Congress%20president.%20Anticipating%20that%20he%20might%20be%20exhausted%20and%20thirsty%2C%20Rahul%20poured%20water%20into%20a%20glass%20and%20offered%20it%20to%20him.%20Some%20Congress%20spokespersons%20tweeted%20about%20this%20gesture.%20On%20another%20occasion%2C%20Rahul%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20personally%20drop%20off%20Kharge%20in%20his%20own%20car%20after%20a%20Congress%20party%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20citing%20these%20instances%20only%20to%20underline%20that%20a%20special%20relationship%20is%20being%20forged%20between%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%20Clearly%2C%20Rahul%20has%20not%20displayed%20such%20respect%20and%20affection%20in%20public%20towards%20any%20other%20veteran%20Congress%20leader.%20This%20has%20some%20serious%20political%20import%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20which%20has%20gathered%20considerable%20momentum%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months.%20As%20a%20veteran%20in%20Indian%20politics%2C%20the%20role%20that%20Kharge%20has%20played%20in%20softening%20the%20rough%20edges%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20quite%20apparent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20has%20much%20more%20going%20in%20his%20favour.%20He%20is%20a%20Dalit%20leader%20from%20the%20South%20and%20does%20not%20threaten%20caste-based%20leaders%20from%20the%20north%20Indian%20Hindi%20heartland%2C%20where%20identity%20politics%20still%20creates%20immense%20hostilities%20over%20turf.%20History%20does%20tell%20us%20that%20whenever%20there%20is%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20decisive%20mandate%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20a%20non-threatening%20leader%20from%20the%20South%20emerges%20as%20a%20consensus%20candidate%20in%20a%20non-BJP%20coalition.%20Of%20course%2C%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20apply%20to%20a%20BJP-led%20coalition%2C%20because%20it%20is%20a%20largely%20north%20Indian%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao%20emerged%20as%20the%20consensus%20PM%20candidate%20after%20the%20Congress%20fell%20short%20of%20a%20majority%20in%201991.%20Within%20the%20Congress%2C%20there%20were%20more%20powerful%20leaders%20from%20the%20North%20but%20the%20relatively%20low-profile%20Narasimha%20Rao%20emerged%20as%20a%20consensus%20candidate.%20The%20same%20could%20be%20said%20about%20dark%20horse%20Deve%20Gowda%2C%20whom%20both%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20supported%20to%20lead%20the%20United%20Front%20coalition.%20Neither%20of%20these%20leaders%20threatened%20cowbelt%20political%20equations%20in%20any%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20importance%20must%20be%20underlined%20as%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20goes%20into%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20If%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20base%20case%20improves%20to%20above%20100%20seats%2C%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20could%20throw%20up%20surprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%202024%20is%20not%202019%20and%20PM%20Modi%20will%20surely%20be%20judged%20by%20the%20people%20on%20his%2010-year%20performance%2C%20irrespective%20of%20whether%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20an%20alternative%20PM%20candidate.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20voter%20psychology%20was%20to%20give%20Modi%20another%20five%20years.%20But%20this%20time%20round%2C%20many%20Modi%20voters%20may%20also%20think%20that%2010%20years%20is%20a%20long%20time%20for%20a%20leader%20to%20show%20results.%20So%20results%20are%20what%20a%20large%20number%20of%20voters%20will%20look%20for%2C%20a%20noisy%20Hindutva%20campaign%20notwithstanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20with%20optimal%20seat-sharing%20across%20the%20country%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20can%20put%20up%20a%20fight%20if%20the%20election%20is%20purely%20a%20referendum%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%2010%20years%20in%20power%2C%20and%20what%20he%20has%20done%20for%20economic%20and%20social%20welfare%2C%20in%20concrete%20terms.%20There%20is%20clearly%20some%20nervousness%20in%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%95%20a%20desperate%20PM%20is%20publicly%20announcing%20unfilled%20government%20vacancies%20and%20internal%20promotions%20dressed%20up%20as%20new%20jobs!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20need%20not%20project%20a%20PM%20candidate%2C%20but%20the%20message%20could%20be%20gently%20delivered%20that%20if%20the%20Congress%20emerges%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20within%20the%20alliance%2C%20with%20about%20110%20-120%20seats%2C%20then%20Kharge%20could%20emerge%20as%20a%20consensus%20candidate%20to%20lead%20a%20possible%20coalition.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20seems%20to%20be%20mentally%20preparing%20for%20this%20