%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGas%3A%20What%20government%20is%20saying%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Union%20minister%20for%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Anurag%20Thakur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fianuragthakur%2Fstatus%2F1696481717366972674%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eannounced%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20packaged%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9CRakhi%20gift%E2%80%9D%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20auspicious%20occasion%20of%20Onam%20and%20Raksha%20Bandhan%2C%20prime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20he%20is%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98bhai%E2%80%99%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20given%20a%20gift%20to%20the%20millions%20and%20millions%20of%20sisters%20and%20users%20of%20LPG%20cylinders.%20The%20prices%20of%20the%20LPG%20cylinders%20for%20domestic%20use%20has%20been%20brought%20down%20by%20Rs%20200%20per%20cylinder%20for%20each%20and%20every%20user.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2075%20lakh%20new%20gas%20connections%20will%20be%20given%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20scheme%20that%20will%20take%20up%20the%20total%20connections%20to%2010.35%20crores%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELaunched%20on%20May%201%2C%202016%2C%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20or%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-fy23-lpg-refills-under-ujjwala-fell-12-of-beneficiaries-didnt-get-a-single-refill-govt%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3EPMUY%20aimed%20to%20provide%20deposit-free%20LPG%20connections%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20adult%20women%20from%20poor%20households%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20beneficiaries%20they%20are%20already%20getting%20Rs%20200%20subsidy%20as%20DBT%20(Direct%20Benefit%20Transfer)%20with%20each%20refill%20but%20they%20will%20also%20benefit%20with%20