c%20decisions%20in%20the%20sphere%20of%20G20%20competences%2C%20and%20let%20everyone%20say%20the%20rest%20on%20their%20own%20behalf%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lavrov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20and%20China%20agreed%20to%20two%20paragraphs%20regarding%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20in%20the%20Bali%20G20%20declaration%20but%20withdrew%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20G20%20meetings%20chaired%20under%20India%E2%80%99s%20presidency%20have%20had%20%E2%80%9Cchair%E2%80%99s%20summary%20and%20outcome%20documents%E2%80%9D%20in%20lieu%20of%20joint%20statements%2C%20so%20as%20to%20circumvent%20the%20lack%20of%20consensus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Lavrov%2C%20Russian%20ambassador%20to%20India%20Denis%20Alipov%20also%20reiterated%20that%20there%20was%20no%20consensus%20on%20the%20text%20related%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underlined%20that%20Russia%20hoped%20the%20summit%20will%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Chuge%20success%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CObviously%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20complicated.%20There%20is%20no%20consensus%20on%20%5Bthe%20Ukraine%20issue%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alipov%20said%20at%20an%20interactive%20session%20in%20the%20Delhi-based%20Foreign%20Correspondents%E2%80%99%20Club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20no%20consensus%20on%20only%20one%20issue%20and%20there%20is%20consensus%20on%20all%20other%20issues%2C%20what%20shall%20we%20do%20in%20this%20situation%3F%E2%80%9D%20Alipov%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20should%20remove%20the%20non-consensual%20issue%20from%20the%20agenda%20to%20agree%20on%20other%20very%20topical%20issues%20such%20as%20climate%20change%2C%20sustainable%20development%2C%20financial%20crisis%20%5Band%5D%20food%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlipov%20suggested%20that%20there%20are%20bodies%20like%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20which%20should%20deliberate%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20and%20that%20Russia%20is%20open%20for%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E